        {
            "title": "北車商場傳由新光三越得標險勝 台鐵最快下周釐清爭議公布結果",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sG6uPFZu2baEIML2AjLNXw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/020575063bf4096a7ad6849c12b506ed\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8C%97%E8%BB%8A%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%82%B3%E7%94%B1%E6%96%B0%E5%85%89%E4%B8%89%E8%B6%8A%E5%BE%97%E6%A8%99%E9%9A%AA%E5%8B%9D-%E5%8F%B0%E9%90%B5%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E9%87%90%E6%B8%85%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C-114220664.html",
